text: Denisse Astrid van Lamoen is an archer from Chile. Lamoen was born on 12 September 1979 in Arica. She competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Denisse van LamoenDenisse VAN LAMOEN == References == Category:Chilean archers Category:Olympians for Chile Category:People from Arica Category:1979 births Category:Living people
